Namespace PluginLiveSkin

Presentation

This plugin of 3D Viewer (flux-three) allows to dynamically controls material of object directly from a 3D viewer.

Usage in Flux

Provide the Object3D that needs to be controlled dynamically as input to this plugin rather to the input of the 3D viewer.

Technical details

The plugin create different 3D objects (different sins) from the input that are forwarded to the parent module (3d viewer).
